description: "A late 18th century maritime navigation map of the straits east of Java, with drawings of the elevations of the straits. The map is also marked with routes of explorers, including the return of Captain Cook’s HMS Endeavour from Australia in 1770."
title: "A   New   Chart   of   the   Eastern   Straits   or   the   Straits   of   the   East   of   Java,   with   a   part   of   the   Banda   Sea;   corrected   and   improved   chiefly   from   the   observation   of   Captn.   -   Williams."
